<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśākābdēbdhinaṁdadyumaṇiparimitē śuklapakṣē nabhasyē rākāyāṁ sōma
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vārē sakaḷaguṇagaṇālaṁkṛtō jhāḍupālaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> prādādācaṁdratāraṁ vimalataraya
<lb n="3" break="no"/>śāḥ puṇyasaṁtāna vṛ(ṁ)dyai śrīmatsiṁhādracūḍāmaṇinaraharayē caṁdraśubhrā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tapatraṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē 1294 va<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ṣa bhādrapada pau<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>nnamī sōmavārē dhanaṁjayagōtrajāta gōpā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷanāyakaṁkara putra jhāḍupālapaḍirāya Apaṇaṁki Āyurārōgyaisvaryyasaṁtā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nābhivṛdhyarttha śrīnarasiṁganātadēvaṁkara Ubhayadhūpē dūyi beḍāsamaya mā 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>sōtsava va<unclear>r</unclear>ṣōtsava<unclear>sa</unclear>mayē dhavaḷacatradaricā Arttē śrīnarsiṁgunātadēvaṁkara śrī
<lb n="8" break="no"/>bhaṁḍārē padmanidhigaṁḍamāḍa dasa dēĪ nityapaḍi dūyi kuṁcā bhātani nibhaṁ
<lb n="9" break="no"/>dha samasyāye pīṭhabarisapaḍibattana vṛttikari saṁpādi cellumaṁcunāyaka
<lb n="10" break="no"/>rapō tiruvaḍināyakaki Ācaṁdrā<unclear>rkka</unclear>kari dhilla <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> dhavaḷacatrapa<unclear>tti</unclear> barise kiṇivu Ata
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṁḍarē gaṁḍamāḍēka dillē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <unclear>bha</unclear>ḷakēnakha dille Aḍābhātabaṁdhyā dharice <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmmuvu
<lb n="12"/>śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpi kṛtō dharmmaḥ pālanīyō mānīṣibhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatrurēva hi śatru
<lb n="13" break="no"/>syāddharmmaśśatrurnna kasya<unclear>cit</unclear> śrī śrī śrī śrī śrī
</p>

